This repository is a derivative work and GitHub fork of:
https://github.com/szvone/Vmq

Upstream project name: Vmq
Upstream author: vone

This repository is not an official upstream repository.

Major changes in this repository include:
- Rewriting the server side in Go
- Replacing the original storage/runtime choices with PostgreSQL and Docker-based deployment
- Preserving part of the original frontend pages, static assets, and API compatibility behavior
- Adding security hardening for authentication, callback validation, proxy handling, and admin endpoints

